{"tid":564701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英聞記者身份即收線","createTime":"2018-02-18T09:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T12:04:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2ab5f8b5f9c987221959e6da937a3f4a766507","tid":564701,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"前特首梁振英2014年被指收取澳洲公司UGL 5000萬元，收款時間橫跨其特首任期，事件發生至今3年。有傳媒昨晚深夜（17日）引述消息，稱律政司已作決定，不會就事件採取法律檢控行動。律政司今早發聲明澄清，未就UGL事件是否檢控作任何決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》今早11時致電梁振英查詢有關事宜，梁振英「喂」了一聲接聽電話，其後記者表明身份，梁振英馬上收線，未有回應任何提問。"},{"pid":"078b771e6794021a62f1cd5c2b2b8fbc56698e40","tid":564701,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"59a0b80fd74b32037608d356253150abdfb1cb51","tid":564701,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"心虛心有鬼"},{"pid":"f4d36df2e1c2c33bcb488058428eaca26753a678","tid":564701,"uid":104613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa25b05e5f77206e87bfef1e1c73f93b2a3abb5c","tid":564701,"uid":78222,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"自己友都cut線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301eb3e10876852d30f2b169ccc8e54be198eb0c","tid":564701,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d36df2e1c2c33bcb488058428eaca26753a678","tid":564701,"uid":104613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"網媒都係記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5421f399b9a17697519c6a693d7e9b1db2238e","tid":564701,"uid":50872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa25b